column5: Stopped in on the way home. Mostly full of suckers with the odd walleye here and there and what looked like one sturgeon swimming around. I think the run is mostly done.
did you get a photo of the sturgeon  most likely the mnr would like to see simcoe sturgeon
Unfortunately no and it was too far down to really make it out with a camera.
If its over then it was a short one- nothing there last weekend, not even suckers...

Talked to a CO there a few years back. He said the numbers had really fallen. I used to look forward to a drive over there to check out the eyes under the dam. I have stopped going because they just aren't there anymore like they used to be and I can see all the suckers I want down here in the Lake O tribs.
